As clarification, in Lguk with one chanter and 2 50+ aoers, the chanter was chain stunning, with 3 aoe stuns as one cast the next came up and the mobs never got a chance to hit the tank, of course stuns were resisted but a couple of secs later the next stun was hitting.<br>
<br>
This was with pulling 6-7 mobs at a time, from frenzy, Magi and Lord.<br>
<br>
The higher the mobs the more chance of resists of course but with 3 or even 4 chanters in a multi raid group doing nothing but stunning I bet you would get long moments of zero dmg from the mobs.<br>
<br>
